ukui-power-manager (2.0.1-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * New upstream release.
    - Fix the focus issue.
    - Fix the wrong layout in English.
    - Fix the wrong popup place in multi-screen.
    - Update the icon at the beginning.
    - Adjust the right-click menu.
    - Adjust the style.
    - Add support for device addition/removal.
    - Add charging effects.
    - Show icon when battery is charging.
    - Alway show predict time.

